name: Fornax Void - TO THE TOP
description: Cybernetic Tissue and Cell Monitor, GIF animation created with Grafx2 in 2015. 330 frames. Custom 256 colors palette. 320px * 180px native resolution upscaled to Full HD. Audio recorded in April 2021 using Waldorf Microwave 1 REV A, E-mu Morpheus, REA YM3812 (OPL2) and Roland JV-2080. 11 seconds Animation Loop, 22 seconds Audio Loop (174.546 BPM). TO THE TOP is a cheat code to the 1993 Bullfrog game Syndicate.
